race.description: Become A Brc Member Maiden Plate
race.comment: Looks a race with a bunch of chances. BY THE WAY (7) was well found on debut but just ran into a couple better on that occasion. Will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience and can improve enough to take this out. QUEEN JEDDAH (12) resumes here but the form she displayed in her first campaign was good enough for a race of this calibre. Tuned up for this with a recent trial win and expecting a bold return. I AM LOUIE (2) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Gollan barn. Keep very safe. MYTHOLOGY (11) will find this easier than recent NSW efforts and looks a must for the multiples. PROPHET OF DESTINY (5) next in line despite the sticky draw.
